dct_title_s: Map of Jersey City, Hudson County, N.J. - June 1881
dct_description_sm: Map shows Commissioners line for solid filling and exterior pier line. The current water line is marked in blue. Water features include Tidewater Basin and Morris Canal Basin. Land features include Central RR of NJ, Bedloe's Island and Ellis Island.
